>  Over 20 countries from Africa and Asia have committed to make education their priority and to transform their education systems to deliver results.

The Commission published a [Progress Report](http://educationcommission.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Commission-2017-Progress-Report.pdf
) that was presented at the UN General Assembly on Sept 20, 2017: p.10: "The leadership of over 20 countries have agreed to take additional steps to increase their commitments to education and implement critical reforms."
